	* n3_parser.y (n3_qname_to_uri):
	Handle NULL (":" in N3) returning the default
	namespace.  It's not quite clear if this is legal.

	* n3_parser.y (raptor_n3_generate_statement):
	Do nothing if some part of the triple
	is NULL.

